text: Jiang Xinyu and Tang Qianhui were the two-time defending champions, but lost in the semifinals to Peng Shuai and Zhang Shuai. Wang Xinyu and Zhu Lin won the title, defeating Peng and Zhang in the final, 6–2, 7–6(7–5). ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Draw Jiangxi International Women's Tennis Open - Women's Doubles 2019 Women's Doubles
